        "func": "let temp = flow.get(\"latest_temp\") || 0;\nlet hum = flow.get(\"latest_hum\") || 0;\nlet soil = flow.get(\"latest_soil\") || 0;\nlet mode = flow.get(\"latest_mode\") || \"Unknown\";\nlet fan = flow.get(\"latest_fan\") || \"Unknown\";\n\nmsg.payload = {\n    timestamp: new Date().toLocaleString(),\n    temperature: parseFloat(temp),\n    humidity: parseFloat(hum),\n    soil_moisture: parseInt(soil),\n    system_mode: mode,\n    fan_state: fan\n};\n\nreturn msg;",
